    "description": "Monsters ‘til Midnight is an arcade-inspired steampunk survival game all about powering up!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Weapons and Abilities</h2><br>From weaponized cucumber sandwiches to explosive crumpets, wield a diverse arsenal of both automatic, and manually aimed weaponry. Augment them with various powers and special abilities to make each run feel unique and challenging.<br><br>Aquire gold to purchase permanent upgrades that will further boost your destructive power.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/b1534a2d423d6c5bc87615153d97eef5.poster.avif?t=1698878918\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/b1534a2d423d6c5bc87615153d97eef5.webm?t=1698878918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/b1534a2d423d6c5bc87615153d97eef5.mp4?t=1698878918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Work towards unlocking new playable characters, new zones, and devastating secret weapons each time you play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/d33ac9230ad10436caec703aec9d4c81.avif?t=1698878918\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br>Discover, equip, and trigger potent active abilities. Whether it’s the defensive dodge roll, or devastating chimney brush attack, there’s something for every playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Local Co-op</h2><br>Join forces with a friend and play locally in 2 player co-op!* XP is shared between both players, so power up and fight the hordes of darkness together. If overwhelmed, spend a level upgrade to revive your teammate. <br><br>*<i>A controller is required for local multiplayer.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/93803916be35831fe2a1085cf0a46416.poster.avif?t=1698878918\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/93803916be35831fe2a1085cf0a46416.webm?t=1698878918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/93803916be35831fe2a1085cf0a46416.mp4?t=1698878918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat Time Itself</h2><br>Survive the ceaseless enemy onslaught until midnight, and face the deathly chimes of the death clocks! Can you defeat time itself?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/bba61ea95e97463a9e61d7d173807c48.poster.avif?t=1698878918\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/bba61ea95e97463a9e61d7d173807c48.webm?t=1698878918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157250/extras/bba61ea95e97463a9e61d7d173807c48.mp4?t=1698878918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Switch between auto-aim and twin-stick aiming on the fly<br></li><li>Over 50 weapons and upgrades to unlock and combine<br></li><li>Equip one of 8 unique active abilities that can be triggered at will to help in the heat of the action<br></li><li>Unlock a cast of 12 distinct and quirky characters to play as such as a dog in a smoking jacket, and a mustache-wearing ghost <br></li><li>Play alone, or co-op with a friend in local multiplayer (<i>A controller is required for local multiplayer</i>)\t<br></li><li>Discover 18 powerful secret weapon combinations<br></li><li>Purchase and experiment with 21 permanent upgrades to suit your play-style<br></li><li>Uncover secret conditions required to face powerful zone bosses</li></ul>",
